Here is what I experienced just recently.  We were at a fairly famous
investigation spot.  The group before us were &quot;releasing&quot; the spirits. 
Funny how we got soooo many evp&#39;s just a few minutes after the spirits
were &quot;helped&quot; by this group.  Leads me to feel that we are just making
ourselves feel good about ourselves for &quot;helping&quot; them over.  I don&#39;t
think we can help a lot of those spirits.  They are there for a
reason...they need to work out some sort of karma...and when that
happens...they can continue.

I&#39;m just saying,
Carol B.









